snippet.title: Abusive Famous couple:  Johnny Depp was sent to hospital by Amber Heard. Her Leaked audio admitting
snippet.description:
How Women like  Amber Heard and her vegan diet cause misery.  Some vegans lose control of their emotions and become violent.  They're doing veganism wrong.

The ACTUAL truth is now coming out about Amber Heard's marriage and divorce to Johnny Depp.

Update: DeFranko has made a video about this
https://youtu.be/T5PKXaMpKzo

Johnny Depp's Diet 

A focus on nutrient density of food item and based on that only, he makes his choice.  His diet routine generally consists of copious food items such as white fish, lean protein such as chicken breast, cottage cheese, green veggies, wheat pasta, soy products etc.

He precisely abides by low calorie food items such as, less sugary fruits, green veggies, whole grains, nuts, seeds etc. The health conscious actor steers clear from sugary and alcoholic beverages and prefers green tea. At times, when he has to lose weight, the sex symbol actor banks on green tea.

Lately, after being inspired by his girlfriend, Amber Heard, Johnny has been following vegan diet plan and is feeling extremely flattered with its rewarding outcomes. He eats six small meals in a day. And to magnify the  lean muscles in his body, he consumes protein supplements with his meals.

Johnny Depp  (Gives millions to charity. He even donated ex-wive Amber Heard's divorce settlement of $7 million to charity)

Amber Heard 
- an ambassador for women's rights and outspoken domestic abuse advocate

#AmberHeardIsAnAbuser

 She was awarded $7 million in the divorce agreement.  She would donate that money to the American Civil Liberties Union, with a focus on battling violence against women, and Children’s Hospital of Los Angeles, where she has volunteered for 10 years

How can a vegan diet cause people to lose control of their emotions and become violent?
*  Eating too little calories.
*  Not only is she vegan, but she's an ACTRESS (wants to be skinny)

Get my ebook about Diet truths & lies
*  "Escape the Diet Matrix"

UPDATE:
Amber Heard uses:
Alcohol, and other substances
Prescription Amphetamines ... which have appetite-suppressing capabilities.

Symptoms:
mood swings
insomnia
grandiosity, or an exaggerated sense of one's own importance
In rare cases, psychosis may occur

From MedicalNewsToday:
"Fears of Amphetamines  side effects and its potential for addiction and abuse caused them to fall out of favor for this purpose. In the 1950s, reports of malnutrition, psychosis, and depression on withdrawal caused doctors to stop prescribing amphetamines for weight loss."
